        "description": {
            "value": "<p>@Template[type:cone|distance:15]</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You telepathically assail the minds of your foes. You deal mental damage equal to 2d4 plus your spellcasting ability modifier to all enemies in the area, with a basic Will save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage increases by [[/r 1d4]]{1d4}.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Amp</strong> You increase the area of the spell to your choice of a @Template[type:cone|distance:30] or @Template[type:cone|distance:60], and the damage dice for the spell change to d10s. Creatures that fail are @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Stupefied]{Stupefied 1} until the start of your next turn (or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Stupefied]{Stupefied 2} on a critical failure).</p>"
